headline: Net Neutrality Day: Cloudflare + Fight for the Future
keywords: Cloudflare Apps, Community, Freedom of Speech, Legal, Net Neutrality, Developers, Politics
description: For Net Neutrality Day on July 12, Fight for the Future launched a Cloudflare App installable for websites all over the world. Sites with it installed saw as many as 178M page views prompting the users to write to their local congressional representative on the importance of Net Neutrality.
